# Raw pilot outputs -- activations at ALL layers for hundreds of problems
# serialize to well over 100MB of JSON (GitHub's hard per-file limit), so
# these are regenerated locally/in Colab and shared out-of-band (Drive/LFS),
# not committed. Plots (*.png) and the fitted oracle_model.joblib are small
# and ARE tracked -- only the raw per-problem activation dumps are excluded.
pilot/pilot_*.jsonl
